[I]Hey Everyone,

Just a kind request when posting topics...

If you are disclosing something specific about the game please post a "SPOILERS" warning in your topic or in the message body itself before you spill the beans.  

Many have not yet finished the game (or are just getting started) and are here seeking help and comments on the game.  Reading about the plot on accident while browsing a topic that has no notification that spoilers are present is disappointing.

Thanks everyone!    :D

tige

P.S.  To the Larian folks...any chance on creating a "spoilers only" sub-forum so topics containing spoilers can be moved?

